sawfowl.regionguard.api.events

Interface RegionAPIPostEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.spongepowered.api.event.Event
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RegionAPIPostEvent.CompleteLoadRegions, RegionAPIPostEvent.PostAPI

    public interface RegionAPIPostEvent
extends org.spongepowered.api.event.Event
    This interface is designed to access the plugin's API and check status.
    Use the child interface RegionAPIPostEvent.PostAPI to access the plugin API.
    Use the child interface RegionAPIPostEvent.CompleteLoadRegions to start working with the regions.
